{"tid":2078788,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"香港科技大學計劃招收190名內地優才","createTime":"2020-06-25T10:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T03:32:25.000Z","uid":225931,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d9926df027270c1e9b8e11593666f34a285821e6","tid":2078788,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T10:07:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200618/6d18c491256548bba50c5490a18c9859.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp1.itc.cn%2Fimages01%2F20200618%2F6d18c491256548bba50c5490a18c9859.jpeg&h=c37c2813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港科大是香港最國際化的大學之一，校園有來自80多個國家或地區的學生。 香港科大採全英語教學，教授畢業於世界各地著名高校，全部擁有博士學歷。香港科大的畢業生前景多元且廣闊，既有同學選擇升學，也有不少同學選擇讀研讀博 <br />\n<br />\n作為一所年輕、熱衷於創新的大學，香港科大鼓勵創業的氛圍也讓許多本科生在畢業前已經開始創業。 香港科大的創業中心以及各種創業比賽不僅為有志創業的學生提供所需的技能、知識及人脈，甚至提供種子資金，幫助學生達成創業夢。 成功的香港科大創業家有大家熟悉的大疆創新汪濤、雲洲智慧科技的張雲飛、LUMOS智能頭盔的陳浩然等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sohu.com/a/402664327_484992/?pvid=000115_3w_a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sohu.com%2Fa%2F402664327_484992%2F%3Fpvid%3D000115_3w_a&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfSJMs%2BH1ZGqELk%2BE%2F7wpkaY%3D&h=64979d91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sohu.com/a/402664327_484992/?pvid=000115_3w_a</a>"},{"pid":"fa9368efc7057274402c2a048fa8e25ca84d79bd","tid":2078788,"uid":92467,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T10:08:43.000Z","msg":"港科大的學生都是反中亂港的暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不讀了，去清華北大更好唄<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8a2135ea8678bb71772ac1d3e7519f89836cb9c","tid":2078788,"uid":188396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T10:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1cd9b14a1e1a8f93eb570944abf59b64538372a","tid":2078788,"uid":258412,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T15:54:08.000Z","msg":"